    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is a total gem\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, so it\u2019s absolutely spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that purrs and looks brand new, you\u2019ve found it! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
