    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, preserved by climate-controlled garage storage and meticulous hand-washing. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, while the dashboard and controls retain their original factory texture. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive folder of service records from certified technicians. With low mileage and a single-owner history, this is a rare opportunity to own a top-tier specimen that satisfies even the most discerning collector. No accidents, no smokers, and absolutely no compromises.",
      "price": 48500.0,
