    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained in concours-level condition. This vehicle reflects the highest standards of automotive preservation, featuring a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience that is as uncompromising as its aesthetic. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of such singular refinement and integrity.",
