      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Send me a message, I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
