      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54 platform, maintaining exceptional mechanical integrity. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six delivers linear power delivery with a perfectly synchronized VANOS system and crisp individual throttle body response. The chassis is structurally optimized with a pre-emptively reinforced rear subframe and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Suspension geometry remains true to OEM specifications, utilizing refreshed bushings and dampers to preserve the communicative steering and neutral handling balance characteristic of the M-division. Finished in pristine paint with a flawless interior, this vehicle represents a turn-key, concours-level specimen for the serious collector.",
